  "session": "session-26",
  "dmNotes": "SET-PIECE 2 — the blind fight. The gimmick: DARKVISION DOESN'T HELP. The room isn't dark, it's FULL — thousands of hanging bones and trinkets physically block sight, while whatever's in here doesn't need eyes. Rules in 'How It Works'.\n\nThe pawn upstairs told them none of it is real and they can walk right through. That lie is why they'll be deep in the gallery before the first thing touches them.\n\nENEMIES: yours to place from the map — whatever you drop in, give it blindsight 60 ft. This scene runs the room, not the roster.\n\nFIRE IS THE INTENDED OUT. If a player burns the strings, reward it hard.",
