  "transition": {
    "crossfadeMs": 2500
  },
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Art Room"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "hang",
          "label": "▶ hang"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "dungeon",
          "label": "〜 dungeon",
          "fadeInMs": 3000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The doorway opens into a room you cannot see the far wall of, because the room is full."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Threads hang from the ceiling — thousands of them: cords, wires, gut, braided hair — and from every one hangs something small. "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "Sounds Dogs Love - Wood Chimes - Videos For Dogs",
          "label": "〜 wood chimes",
          "fadeInMs": 3000
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " A finger bone. A ring. A milk tooth. A coin, a buckle, a lock of hair tied with ribbon, a child's carved animal, a knucklebone, a knucklebone, a knucklebone. They hang at every height, in rows and drifts and curtains, on and on into the dark past where your light reaches."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "And they "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "move",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "italic"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". The air shifts, and ten thousand small hard things turn on their strings and touch each other, and the whole room makes a sound like rain on dry leaves that never quite stops."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": []
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How It Works"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "Heavily obscured by OBJECTS, not darkness", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " — darkvision does nothing, light spells do nothing. You can't see through ten thousand hanging bones." }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "- Everyone is effectively " },
            { "type": "text", "text": "blinded", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " beyond 5 ft" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "- " },
            { "type": "text", "text": "Attacking unseen:", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " disadvantage, and you must guess the space — wrong guess is an auto-miss" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "- " },
            { "type": "text", "text": "Attacked by something unseen:", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " attacker has advantage" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "- " },
            { "type": "text", "text": "Movement", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " through the gallery is difficult terrain" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "- " },
            { "type": "text", "text": "Noise gives you away:", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " move more than 5 ft on your turn and you're heard — your space is known to everything until your next turn" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "- " },
            { "type": "text", "text": "Finding by ear:", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] },
            { "type": "text", "text": " action — Perception vs. Stealth. Success pinpoints until it moves." }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            { "type": "text", "text": "Whatever you place in here: give it blindsight 60 ft.", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }] }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Fight"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "stalk",
          "label": "▶ stalk"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- Off to the left, the sound changes — a patch of the rain-on-leaves noise goes hard and fast, a whole curtain of bone swinging at once. Then stops."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- Then the same thing behind you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- Then close."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "fight",
          "label": "▶ fight"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- Make them declare which square they swing at - Describe enemy positions by sound only - Reinforcements arrive as new sound from a direction that was quiet"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Burning It"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "burn",
          "label": "▶ burn"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " "
        },
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "amb",
          "ref": "nox-fire-big",
          "label": "〜 nox-fire-big",
          "volume": 0.4,
          "fadeInMs": 2000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The intended clever answer",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " — gut, hair, cord and dry cloth take fire "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "instantly",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "italic"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Don't hint; let a player find it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- Within a round the hangings fall — obscurement "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "gone",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " - Burning debris: anything in the open takes "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "1d6 fire",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " at the end of its turn for 2–3 rounds"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "After"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "cue",
          "kind": "music",
          "ref": "after",
          "label": "▶ after"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- Very quiet. If it burned: ash, small blackened things, a smell that won't leave their clothes. If not: the strings still turning, drifts of torn-down keepsakes underfoot."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "One real find — Investigation DC 15, only if they search the drifts:",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " a "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ring of Protection",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", hanging on a thread like everything else. Otherwise no treasure."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Past the far side: the stair down. Switch to "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "'Eekso — The Ritual'",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}